69th Street, east side, north from and across Juniper Valley Road, showing (left) the Ferguson House, built about 1840, and the former District School No. 6 (right), the latter being at the N. E. corner of Juniper Valley Road. 69th Street, here, was formerly named Juniper Avenue.
